# Plexichat Server Requirements
# Direct dependencies only. Run `uv pip compile requirements.in --generate-hashes -o requirements.txt`
# to generate the fully-pinned requirements.txt with integrity hashes.
#
# Optional system dependencies:
# - ffmpeg/ffprobe: Required for video metadata extraction (duration, resolution)
#   Install via: apt install ffmpeg (Linux), brew install ffmpeg (macOS),
#   or download from https://ffmpeg.org/download.html (Windows)
#   Without ffprobe, video uploads work but metadata won't be extracted.
#
# - aiortc dependencies: opus, srtp, libvpx for WebRTC media codecs
#   Linux: apt install libopus-dev libsrtp2-dev libvpx-dev
#   macOS: brew install opus srtp libvpx
#   Windows: Download pre-built binaries or use vcpkg

